data.description:
Spacious 4 bed, 2.5 bath home located on an oversized corner lot in 1604 and Potranco Rd area. Custom window plantation shutters throughout the home. Living area, dining area and island kitchen create large open floor plan perfect for entertaining or large gatherings. Entry room can be used as formal dining area or office/study. Kitchen features granite countertops and stainless-steel over-range microwave and dishwasher. Refrigerator conveys. Downstairs primary bedroom with high tray ceiling, ensuite bathroom with double sink vanity and linen closet and large walk-in closet with extra shelving. Three secondary bedrooms and laundry room located upstairs along with large second living area.

All occupants 18+ must apply. Application is at peoplefirstrealestate.com, in top menu select Residential - Rent. This property will be managed by the Landlord after leasing.
